      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a collector-grade example of the legendary S54-powered platform. The high-revving 3.2L inline-six features individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing, delivering linear power to a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. This specimen has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including rod bearing replacement and rear subframe reinforcement, ensuring structural and mechanical longevity. The suspension retains factory geometry with crisp damping, and the variable M-differential lock provides optimal torque distribution. Finished in Carbon Black with a flawless Nappa leather interior, the vehicle displays no signs of heat cycling or oxidative fatigue. A mechanically pristine masterpiece for the discerning purist.",
